          </p>
          <p>
            For example, codecs (can) be installed on Ubuntu during the initial install, however with Fedora, an external repository is required.
            Likewise, proprietary video drivers are installed as part of the SteamOS install process, but take many additional steps for setup on Debian.
          </p>
